reviewText: I think I have a new hobby and that is watching Swamp People. This is a great series and I am enjoying it thoroughly. It was certainly a nice gift from my spouse - who thinks I am a little crazy, I believe, but I am slowly hooking him to the Swamp People, too. This is a great series with lots of exciting action and truly the producers selected the best of the best for this set. I plan on watching it over and over. I always see something new in it. I particularly enjoy the scenery and the other wildlife. The birds are spectacular in this series. This is just really enjoyable to me and I feel like I have a bunch of new friends down in the swamp.
I truly enjoyed this collection. The best of the exploits of these brave hunters.  I love seeing their adventures.  Thank you for sending this quickly. Arrived in perfect condition.
